		"name": "Horse Racing - Financial Refunds Comprehensive Test Suite",
		"description": "Comprehensive E2E Postman test suite to verify the 4 newly implemented financial refund flows on the backend. This suite contains registration, activation, login, dynamic wallet creation, mock deposits, connections management, horse creation, tournament setup, and testing scenarios for Jockey reject (Flow 1), Admin reject (Flow 2), Admin confirm/lock (Flow 3), and Admin cancel tournament (Flow 4) with Spectator bet refunds.",
